<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 06:09:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>法国总统马克龙抵达以色列；两名老年人质从加沙获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-live/two-elderly-israeli-hostages-freed-from-gaza-frances-macron-to-visit-israel-ramallah/0000018b-5f5d-d2b2-addf-7f7dcd790000</link><description>法国总统马克龙抵达以色列，预计会见内塔尼亚胡、赫尔佐格和人质家属 ■ 两名被哈马斯囚禁的老年妇女获释 ■ 军队袭击真主党小组，北部边境局势再度紧张 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少造成 1,300 人死亡 ■ 哈马斯控制卫生部：4,380名巴勒斯坦人死亡，13,000人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 04:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-live/two-elderly-israeli-hostages-freed-from-gaza-frances-macron-to-visit-israel-ramallah/0000018b-5f5d-d2b2-addf-7f7dcd790000</guid></item><item><title>在黎巴嫩，平民听到以色列的战争威胁，但无处可逃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/in-lebanon-civilians-hear-israeli-threats-of-war-but-have-nowhere-to-turn/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff3622b20000</link><description>对于因预期以色列和真主党之间的冲突升级而逃离黎巴嫩南部的平民来说，贝鲁特缺乏正常运作的政府使生活变得更加困难</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 03:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/in-lebanon-civilians-hear-israeli-threats-of-war-but-have-nowhere-to-turn/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff3622b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙地面进攻之前进行了一场令人紧张的等待游戏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-plays-a-nerve-wracking-waiting-game-ahead-of-a-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff36c1350000</link><description>加沙地面行动的拖延加剧了政府与军队之间以及政府内部的信任危机 ■ 在释放两名以色列老年妇女后，哈马斯希望部分释放人质能够减轻其面临的国际压力在下面</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 03:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-plays-a-nerve-wracking-waiting-game-ahead-of-a-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff36c1350000</guid></item><item><title>“安德森·库珀说：我有一段你被绑架儿子的视频”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-24/ty-article-podcast/anderson-cooper-said-i-have-a-video-of-your-kidnapped-son/0000018b-5e1a-d8e2-a1eb-ff1e67b50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 22:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-24/ty-article-podcast/anderson-cooper-said-i-have-a-video-of-your-kidnapped-son/0000018b-5e1a-d8e2-a1eb-ff1e67b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的首要任务必须是释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-top-priority-must-be-to-free-the-hostages/0000018b-5e35-d473-a5fb-7efd82530000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 21:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-top-priority-must-be-to-free-the-hostages/0000018b-5e35-d473-a5fb-7efd82530000</guid></item><item><title>不要让对哈马斯复仇的呼声压制我们的良心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dont-let-calls-for-revenge-against-hamas-silence-our-conscience/0000018b-5d90-d8e2-a1eb-ff966bca0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 21:19:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dont-let-calls-for-revenge-against-hamas-silence-our-conscience/0000018b-5d90-d8e2-a1eb-ff966bca0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-5e5e-d2b2-addf-7e7e496f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 21:10:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-5e5e-d2b2-addf-7e7e496f0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列老年妇女在被哈马斯囚禁 17 天后获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/two-elderly-israeli-women-released-from-hamas-captivity-after-17-days/0000018b-5e18-d307-adbb-7f387a240000</link><description>10 月 7 日，这两名妇女，85 岁的 Yocheved Lifshitz 和 79 岁的 Nurit Cooper，被哈马斯恐怖分子从尼尔奥兹基布兹带走。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 20:02:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/two-elderly-israeli-women-released-from-hamas-captivity-after-17-days/0000018b-5e18-d307-adbb-7f387a240000</guid></item><item><title>接近内塔尼亚胡的官员呼吁推迟加沙地面行动，匿名社交媒体活动也纷纷效仿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/officials-close-to-pm-call-for-delay-of-gaza-ground-op-social-media-campaign-follows-suit/0000018b-5d5f-d8e2-a1eb-ff5fc8390000</link><description>政治消息来源质疑这些信息的传播是否表明内塔尼亚胡正在试图为推迟甚至避免在加沙地带进行大规模地面行动做好舆论准备</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 18:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/officials-close-to-pm-call-for-delay-of-gaza-ground-op-social-media-campaign-follows-suit/0000018b-5d5f-d8e2-a1eb-ff5fc8390000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院将于 2024 年 2 月就以色列在巴勒斯坦领土上的行为的后果举行听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/world-court-to-hold-hearings-on-consequences-of-israeli-practices-in-palestinian-territory/0000018b-5d70-d8e2-a1eb-ff7690810000</link><description>国际法院将于明年二月举行听证会，要求就包括东耶路撒冷在内的被占领土上的做法的法律影响提供咨询意见</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 17:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/world-court-to-hold-hearings-on-consequences-of-israeli-practices-in-palestinian-territory/0000018b-5d70-d8e2-a1eb-ff7690810000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最需要帮助的时刻，内塔尼亚胡的右翼民粹主义朋友去了哪里？</title>