 2023 14:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/could-bidens-support-of-israels-gaza-war-cost-him-the-2024-election/0000018b-5c62-d2b2-addf-7e7a1d6e0000</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列教授警告犹太父母不要让他们的孩子进入美国精英大学</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-professor-is-warning-jewish-parents-to-keep-their-kids-away-from-elite-u-s-colleges/0000018b-5c37-d8e2-a1eb-ff37fcba0000</link><description>哈马斯袭击以色列后，哥伦比亚大学的 Shai Davidai 教授公开表达了美国学术机构的安全担忧。他指责自己的大学校长未能打击校园内支持恐怖分子的学生组织</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 14:00:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-professor-is-warning-jewish-parents-to-keep-their-kids-away-from-elite-u-s-colleges/0000018b-5c37-d8e2-a1eb-ff37fcba0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀之后，创伤治疗将不再一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dealing-with-national-trauma-after-hamas-attack-classic-psychotherapy-is-not-enough/0000018b-3e23-df22-a5eb-3f7b14f20000</link><description>哈马斯的突然袭击让以色列震惊不已。当事件正在进行并且现实感觉不安全时，治疗创伤的传统方法是不够的，但以色列人以同情心对待彼此肯定会有所帮助</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 13:43:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dealing-with-national-trauma-after-hamas-attack-classic-psychotherapy-is-not-enough/0000018b-3e23-df22-a5eb-3f7b14f20000</guid></item><item><title>歌手公开反对哈马斯大屠杀后，麦当娜的安保细节得到升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/madonnas-security-detail-upgraded-after-singer-speaks-out-against-hamas-massacre/0000018b-5c70-d00f-a9bf-7c78761b0000</link><description>这位已经开始全球庆祝巡演的歌手谴责了这起致命袭击，并写道“我的心与以色列同在”，她在社交媒体上受到了严厉的批评。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:55:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/madonnas-security-detail-upgraded-after-singer-speaks-out-against-hamas-massacre/0000018b-5c70-d00f-a9bf-7c78761b0000</guid></item><item><title>破坏者成功地将特拉维夫从地图上抹去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/saboteurs-successfully-erase-tel-aviv-off-the-maps/0000018b-5b9d-d473-a5fb-7fdd33210000</link><description>OpenStreetMap 曾出现过编辑战争，用户反复恢复地图上已删除的部分，并阻止正在删除它们的用户。自第一次删除以来，已有数十次编辑和重建</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/saboteurs-successfully-erase-tel-aviv-off-the-maps/0000018b-5b9d-d473-a5fb-7fdd33210000</guid></item><item><title>在反犹太主义抬头之际，英国犹太人为在加沙被扣押的以色列人质举行集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/british-jews-rally-for-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-amid-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-5c31-d8e2-a1eb-ff37966a0000</link><description>反犹太主义袭击增加了 1,350% 以上，犹太教堂和犹太学校加强了安全措施，但这并没有阻止英国犹太人，他们周日大批参加了伦敦特拉法加广场的示威活动</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/british-jews-rally-for-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-amid-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-5c31-d8e2-a1eb-ff37966a0000</guid></item><item><title>半岛电视台以色列办事处应该关闭吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/should-al-jazeeras-israeli-offices-be-shut-down/0000018b-5c36-d8e2-a1eb-ff36d6f60000</link><description>半岛电视台正在呼应哈马斯的信息，并且在报道上疏忽大意，但这是否证明以色列政府有理由关闭该电视台的运作——正如沙特阿拉伯、埃及和伊拉克已经所做的那样？</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/should-al-jazeeras-israeli-offices-be-shut-down/0000018b-5c36-d8e2-a1eb-ff36d6f60000</guid></item></channel></rss>